<figureCitation id="9A969CDFFF83FFB8FC45FB28FC3CFAA7" box="[925,1020,1274,1300]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[136,229,1883,1905]" captionTargetBox="[206,1380,190,1859]" captionTargetId="figure-17@5.[206,1380,190,1859]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. Clidemia hirta (L.) D.Don: a. flower and fruit. Clidemia urceolata: b. flower. Huberia ovalifolia: c. flower; d. fruits. Leandra reversa: e. inflorescence. Marcetia taxifolia: f. flowers. Miconia albicans: g. fruits and floral buds. Miconia calvescens: h. flowers. Miconia chartacea: i. leaves. Miconia cinnamomifolia: j. branches with interpetiolar pseudo-stipules; k. fruits. Miconia cubatanensis: l. inflorescence. Miconia dodecandra: m. fruits. Miconia prasina: n. inflorescence. Miconia pusilliflora: o. inflorescence. Ossaea marginata: p. flowers; q. fruit. Tibouchina corymbosa: r. fruits. Tibouchina estrellensis: s. flower. Tibouchina gaudichaudiana: t. flower; u. fruit. Tibouchina granulosa: v. flower. Tibouchina heteromalla: x. flower. Tibouchina trichopoda: z. flower." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5149562" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5149562/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="79">Figs. 3o</figureCitation>
